    • queue

      @Nonnull public Cancelable queue(@Nullable String name, @Nonnull Runnable task)
      Queue task for execution and enable the executor for activation if necessary. The task must not be already queued.
      Parameters:
      name - A human consumable name for the task. It should be non-null if Zemeckis.areNamesEnabled() returns true and null otherwise.
      task - the task.
      Returns:
      the Cancelable instance that can be used to cancel execution of the task.
